# Required local game assets

The current code expects these files in the repository root:

- `background.PNG`
- `healthbar.png`
- `Demon.png`
- `Samurai.png`

They are intentionally not included in this public-repository package because
redistribution rights for third-party game art have not been verified.

Add only assets you created yourself or are licensed to redistribute. If you
have permission, copy the four files into the repository root before running.
